        <item>
            <title>《刺客教条：暗影者》黑人武士当主角，预告片负评达 21 万</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/assassins-creed-shadows/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=assassins-creed-shadows</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/assassins-creed-shadows/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 11:00:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ubisoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[刺客教条]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[刺客教条：暗影者]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1236011</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Ubisoft 旗下王牌游戏《刺客教条：暗影者》（Assassin&#8217;s Creed Shadows）推出首条预告片，但影片一出，即时引来网民的批评，影片 Dislike 数量已达 21 万。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">《刺客教条：暗影者》预告片确认男主角为织田信长的黑人家臣「弥助」，而女主角就是伊贺国忍者「奈绪江」。有日本网民指作品太正治正确，亦批评其为文化挪用。更有网民发现，维基百科上有一份在日本获得武士身份的外国人名单，当中未有「弥助」。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">『アサシン クリード シャドウズ』11 月 15 日発売！<br />日本语吹替版の公式シネマティックワールドプレミアトレーラーが公开されました。<br />🎥 <a href="https://t.co/J6NxafGY6F">https://t.co/J6NxafGY6F</a></p><p>Ubisoft+加入者・アルティメットエディション购入者は、12 日よりプレイ可能です。<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/AssassinsCreedShadows?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#AssassinsCreedShadows</a><a href="https://t.co/G1zUYDatxd">pic.twitter.com/G1zUYDatxd</a></p><p>&mdash; Ubisoft Japan (@UBISOFT_JAPAN) <a href="https://twitter.com/UBISOFT_JAPAN/status/1790775605518008677?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">May 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Japanese Reception from Ubisoft&#39;s latest videogame, Assassin&#39;s Creed Shadows.</p><p>One Japanese user says: &quot;For the first time I understood what cultural Appropriation was&quot;</p><p>Very diverse neo-colonialist we have here 💀 <a href="https://t.co/SDnyudjuup">pic.twitter.com/SDnyudjuup</a></p><p>&mdash; LearningTheLaw (@Mangalawyer) <a href="https://twitter.com/Mangalawyer/status/1790895910748107227?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">May 16, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲有日本网民指作品太正治正确，亦批评其为文化挪用</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">So a Wikipedia editor called Theozilla is getting called out for editing Yasuke&#39;s page in an edit war, against Wikipedia&#39;s own policy.</p><p>He keeps insisting Yasuke was a samurai, says he doesn&#39;t need a source, and is responsible for defacing the Yasuke page by deleting stuff&#8230; <a href="https://t.co/pU4Wph4gAf">https://t.co/pU4Wph4gAf</a></p><p>&mdash; Grummz (@Grummz) <a href="https://twitter.com/Grummz/status/1790821830972031314?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">May 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">亦有欧美玩家指戏中描写成武士并不恰当，由于记载「弥助」的日本历史并不多，因此争议不断。有人利用第三方插件观看预告片 Dislike 数，发现高达 21 万个 Dislike。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1236050 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/e4102ee26e24e9dcc4a4-588x580.jpg" alt="" width="588" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/e4102ee26e24e9dcc4a4-588x580.jpg 588w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/e4102ee26e24e9dcc4a4.jpg 840w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 588px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《刺客教条：暗影者》预告片高达 216914 个 Dislike</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://gagadget.com/en/after-the-screening-of-assassins-creed-shadows-players-were-divided-into-two-camps-the-trailer-received-194-thousand-likes-but-more-than-215-thousand-dislikes/">gagadgat</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/assassins-creed-shadows/game-channel/">《刺客教条：暗影者》黑人武士当主角，预告片负评达 21 万</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/assassins-creed-shadows/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
