        </item>
        <item>
            <title>入境处将军澳设新总部，自助服务站增至 10 个</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/immigration-department/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=immigration-department</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/immigration-department/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 10:34:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[入境处]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1236021</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">入境处将军澳新总部将于下月 11 日起提供服务。观塘人事登记办事处申请及领取身份证的最后服务日期为 6 月 8 日，并于 6 月 11 日正式迁往将军澳。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1236023 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240516at-1-2-694x330.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="330" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240516at-1-2-694x330.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240516at-1-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲观塘人事登记办事处下月迁至将军澳</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">观塘人事登记办事处下月迁至将军澳，仍未领取身份证的市民可到观塘临时办事处领取。旅行证件方面，将军澳新总部除了会提供申请特区护照服务，同时会增设办理签证身份书及回港证的申请，届时将军澳新总部将会有 10 部自助服务站。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">助理首席入境事务主任龚国梁：「届时总部搬迁后，申请证件服务站增至 6 部。办事处亦会新增 4 部领取护照服务站，方便市民自助领证，透过增加自助机数目，从而令办事处处理能力大幅提升。我们预计，处理量可提升多达一倍。」</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1753377-20240516.htm?spTabChangeable=0">RTHK</a>、入境处</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/immigration-department/life-tech/smartcity/">入境处将军澳设新总部，自助服务站增至 10 个</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/immigration-department/life-tech/smartcity/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>38 种主机模拟器 RetroArch 上架 App Store   任天堂 + 世嘉 + PS1 + PSP 游戏任玩</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/retroarch-2/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=retroarch-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/retroarch-2/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 10:33:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RetroArch]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SEGA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony PlayStation]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1235937</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>拥有丰富历史和开发背景的多系统游戏主机模拟器 RetroArch，今日正式在 iOS App Store 免费提供下载。这对拥有 Apple 产品的怀旧游戏迷绝对是个好消息，用家在安装 RetroArch 后可以模拟多种经典主机游戏，包括任天堂、SEGA、Sony PlayStation 等。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235938 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240516at-6-694x344.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="344" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240516at-6-694x344.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240516at-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲游戏主机模拟器 RetroArch，今日正式在 iOS App Store 免费提供下载</p><p>RetroArch 过去已在 PC 和 Mac 平台上推出，但由于 Apple 之前对 App Store 的指引，一直未能登陆 iOS 装置，而今日终在 App Store 上架。支援的系统包括：</p><ul><li>Amstrad CPC</li><li>Atari 2600</li><li>Atari 5200</li><li>Atari 7800</li><li>Atari Lynx</li><li>Bandai WonderSwan</li><li>Commodore Amiga</li><li>Commodore 64</li><li>Commodore 128</li><li>Commodore CBM-II</li><li>Commodore PET</li><li>Commodore Plus</li><li>Commodore VIC-20</li><li>ColecoVision</li><li>GCE Vectrex</li><li>Fairchild Channel F</li><li>Mattel Intellivision</li><li>Nintendo Entertainment System / Famicom (NES)</li><li>Super Nintendo Entertainment System (SNES)</li><li>Nintendo Virtual Boy</li><li>Nintendo Game Boy Color</li><li>Nintendo Game Boy Advance</li><li>Nintendo DS</li><li>SNK Neo Geo</li><li>SNK Neo Geo CD</li><li>SNK Neo Geo Pocket</li><li>Sega Master System</li><li>Sega Game Gear</li><li>Sega Genesis / Mega Drive</li><li>Sega CD</li><li>Sega Saturn</li><li>Sharp X68000</li><li>Sony PlayStation 1</li><li>Sony PlayStation Portable (PSP)</li><li>Sinclair ZX Spectrum</li><li>Texas Instruments TI-83</li><li>Thomson MO/TO</li><li>Watara Supervision</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235940 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240516at-8-694x413.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="413" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240516at-8-694x413.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240516at-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple 用家现可用 iPhone、iPad 或 Apple TV 上下载 RetroArch</p><p>此外，RetroArch 完全支援 MFi 控制器，用户可以使用喜爱的蓝牙控制器，在 iPhone 或 iPad 上享受游戏体验。Apple 上月更新 App Store 指引，允许游戏模拟器上架，自此以来，新应用程式陆续推出。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/05/15/retroarch-arrives-on-ios-emulator/">9To5Mac</a>、<a href="https://apps.apple.com/tw/app/retroarch/id6499539433?platform=iphone">App Store</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/07/switch-7/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">任天堂社长预告 Switch 后继机将发布</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/nintendo-switch-2-leaks-backward-compatible/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">网络爆料任天堂 Switch 2   可向后兼容初代游戏卡带</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/28/nintendo-reportedly-looking-to-enter-the-indian-market-officially/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">任天堂一改多年态度，计划进军印度市场</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/retroarch-2/software/ios-app/">38 种主机模拟器 RetroArch 上架 App Store   任天堂 + 世嘉 + PS1 + PSP 游戏任玩</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/retroarch-2/software/ios-app/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>消委会测试垃圾电话拦截 App   2 款会公开通讯录 + 亲友资料或被任睇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/16/callapp-truecaller/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=callapp-truecaller</link>
